Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be better if we go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I found a great spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the entrance, right? If you come in like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's another way down here. If you come down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this place is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many people and there are really a lot of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, it looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also freshwater snails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, these freshwater snails are big.
